## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all recent developments in the field of climate science. Additionally, the complexity of climate systems means that predictions and models can vary, leading to different interpretations of data. Further research and continuous monitoring are necessary to fully understand the long-term impacts of global warming on the environment.

